data.description: Larger than it looks with 2700+ sq Feet.  Beautiful 4 Bedroom 3 Bath Home Located in Sought After North Jackson Elementary and Jackson County High Schools. The main floor features an open floor plan with a chef kitchen opening to the family room and dining area. Kitchen features granite counters, stainless appliances, and an eat at island. The large master suite has a dual vanity, granite counters, and a walk in closet which connects to the laundry room.  There are 2 more bedrooms on the main floor and another full bathroom. Upstairs has a large bedroom and a full bath and is also perfect for a bonus room/media room. Enjoy the peaceful backyard from the covered patio. This home is conveniently located near the schools, shopping, restaurants, and each access to I-85.  Come make this your next home!
